articles.title: The full set of Coldplay at Glastonbury 2024 - BBC.com
articles.description: Coldplay return to Glastonbury for the fifth time. Expect a visual spectacle and a set list full of bangers!
articles.content: Coldplay were the Saturday night headliner at the 2024 Glastonbury Festival. The band is no stranger to the Pyramid Stage top spot. In 2002, they headlined for the first time, with just one album und… [+471 chars]
